<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>CV of {{ profile.fullname }}</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;500;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #f9fafb; margin: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 56rem; margin: 2rem auto; background: white; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(to right, #2563eb, #1e40af); color: white; padding: 2rem; }
        .profile-img { width: 8rem; height: 8rem; border: 4px solid white; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .section { padding: 2rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1d4ed8; border-bottom: 2px solid #bfdbfe; padding-bottom: 0.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .contact-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
        .experience-item { border-left: 4px solid; padding-left: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            {% if app.user.profile.profilePicture is defined %}
                <img src="{{ asset('/uploads/profiles/' ~ app.user.profile.profilePicture) }}" alt="Profile Photo" class="profile-img" >
            {% endif %}
                <h1>{{ profile.fullname }}</h1>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                        </svg>
                        {{ app.user.email }}
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
                        </svg>
                        {{ profile.phone }}
                    </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
        <p style="background: #f3f4f6; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
            [Sample Summary] Experienced professional with demonstrated skills in various technologies.
            Adept at working in team environments to deliver high-quality solutions.
        </p>

        <h2>Experience</h2>
        <div class="experience-item" style="border-color: #3b82f6;">
            <h3>Senior Developer at Example Corp</h3>
            <div class="contact-item">
                <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                </svg>
                January 2020 - Present
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li>Lead development team building enterprise applications</li>
                <li>Implemented CI/CD pipelines</li>
                <li>Mentored junior developers</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-item" style="border-color: #93c5fd;">
            <h3>Junior Developer at Sample Company</h3>
            <div class="contact-item">
                <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                </svg>
                June 2018 - December 2019
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li>Developed business applications</li>
                <li>Collaborated cross-functionally</li>
                <li>Optimized performance</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: start;">
            <div style="background: #dbeafe; padding: 0.75rem; border-radius: 50%;">
                <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>B.Sc. Computer Science</h3>
                <p>State University</p>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                    </svg>
                    2013 - 2017
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>